HEADWORD: medick
<hw>medick</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any of several Old World herbs of the
genus <gen>Medicago</gen> having small flowers and trifoliate compound
leaves.</def> <altsp>[Also spelled <asp>medic</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> trefoil.</syn>⟦br⟧
